Which Notifications Will Be Sent When wfntfqup.sql Is Run?

The notifications what will be sent when running wfntfqup.sql will be those that reside within the wf_notification_out queue.

In the wfntfqup.sql script, the following SQL is used to fill in the mailer queue has that criteria: 

SQL> 

select notification_id, group_id, recipient_role, message_type, message_name, status
from wf_notifications
where status in ('OPEN', 'CANCELED')
and mail_status in ('MAIL', 'INVALID')
and notification_id >= l_firstNotification
and notification_id <= l_lastNotification
order by notification_id;
 

