In other words : 

a. Obtain the HTTP header tracer add-on:

 Internet Explorer (IE): http://www.blunck.se/iehttpheaders.html
 Firefox (FF): http://livehttpheaders.mozdev.org/
 b. Once installed and the browser restarted, start the HTTP header tracing add-on is as follows:

   (IE) View -> Explorer Bar -> ieHTTPheaders v1.6
